name: df-trkgb
params: setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, setvar s3, setvar s4, setvar s5, setvar s6, setvar s7, setvar s8, setvar s9, setvar s10, setvar s11
body: |- wceq(cstrkgb, cab(s0, wsbc(s1, cfv(cbs, cv(s0)), wsbc(s2, cfv(citv, cv(s0)), w3a(wral(s3, cv(s1), wral(s4, cv(s1), wi(wcel(cv(s4), co(cv(s3), cv(s2), cv(s3))), wceq(cv(s3), cv(s4))))), wral(s3, cv(s1), wral(s4, cv(s1), wral(s5, cv(s1), wral(s6, cv(s1), wral(s7, cv(s1), wi(wa(wcel(cv(s6), co(cv(s3), cv(s2), cv(s5))), wcel(cv(s7), co(cv(s4), cv(s2), cv(s5)))), wrex(s8, cv(s1), wa(wcel(cv(s8), co(cv(s6), cv(s2), cv(s4))), wcel(cv(s8), co(cv(s7), cv(s2), cv(s3))))))))))), wral(s9, cpw(cv(s1)), wral(s10, cpw(cv(s1)), wi(wrex(s8, cv(s1), wral(s3, cv(s9), wral(s4, cv(s10), wcel(cv(s3), co(cv(s8), cv(s2), cv(s4)))))), wrex(s11, cv(s1), wral(s3, cv(s9), wral(s4, cv(s10), wcel(cv(s11), co(cv(s3), cv(s2), cv(s4))))))))))))))
comment: Define the class of geometries fulfilling the 3 betweenness axioms in Tarski's Axiomatization of Geometry: identity, Axiom A6 of [Schwabhauser] p. 11, axiom of Pasch, Axiom A7 of [Schwabhauser] p. 12, and continuity, Axiom A11 of [Schwabhauser] p. 13. (Contributed by Thierry Arnoux, 24-Aug-2017.)
